{
  "description": "A nighttime cityscape featuring a vibrant fireworks display over a long, illuminated bridge. The bridge appears to be a modern suspension or cable-stayed structure with evenly spaced lights along its length. Beyond the bridge, a dense urban landscape stretches into the distance, composed of numerous buildings and skyscrapers, many of which are lit up with varying colors. In the far background, a larger, red-lit structure stands out prominently. Above the bridge, the fireworks explode in a dazzling array of colors, including white, green, and red, creating a spectacular visual effect against the dark sky. The water below the bridge is dark and reflects some of the city lights. The overall composition is a wide-angle shot capturing a grand view of the city and its celebratory atmosphere.",
